---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'

const updated = '2026-06-19'
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer — Books" description="What books.oriz.in is and isn't.">
  <div class="spine-prose">
    <header class="page-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">
        <a href="/">CATALOGUE</a> / <a href="/legal/">LEGAL</a> / DISCLAIMER
      </p>
      <h1>Disclaimer.</h1>
      <p class="meta">Last updated · {updated}</p>
    </header>

    <article class="prose">
      <p>
        Everything on books.oriz.in is published in good faith for general
        information only. Use it at your own risk.
      </p>

      <h2>NCERT is the source of truth</h2>
      <p>
        NCERT is the publisher and copyright holder of the textbooks indexed
        here. Books does not host the PDFs — every download button links
        directly to <code>ncert.nic.in</code>. If a download fails, the
        source file at NCERT is the one that's broken; reach out via the
        <a href="/contact/">contact form</a> and we'll either find an
        alternate link or remove the listing.
      </p>

      <h2>Not professional advice</h2>
      <p>
        Books indexes school curriculum material for browsing convenience.
        Nothing here constitutes academic, legal, medical, or career advice.
        Consult a qualified professional for those.
      </p>

      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        Every textbook page links to <code>ncert.nic.in</code> or other
        official sources. We don't control their content or uptime, and
        inclusion is not an endorsement.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Books does not currently use affiliate links. If that ever changes,
        the links will be marked, and this page will be updated.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
